{"tid":1797198,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"旺角金行區 五小時無警巡","createTime":"2019-12-25T08:27:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T00:37:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"224ce40583a956b2a0243f341042effe05851c0a","tid":1797198,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T08:27:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191225/LW7PY3P4XTSM7VCWHFLT37A5DM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191225%2FLW7PY3P4XTSM7VCWHFLT37A5DM%2F&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFNekL701Gi2Y7kfdl15EDb4%3D&h=0a629f1a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191225%2FLW7PY3P4XTSM7VCWHFLT37A5DM%2F&h=8c63562d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191225/LW7PY3P4XTSM7VCWHFLT37A5DM/</a><br />\n<br />\n旺角金行區 五小時無警巡<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】近日搶劫案頻生，除珠寶金行及錶舖外，賊人連快餐店也不放過，可見本港治安每下愈況。記者昨晨在旺角一段金行林立的彌敦道視察，發現五小時內都沒有巡警蹤影。有當區區議員質疑，警方製造「冇警時分」，導致大案件出現。<br />\n<br />\n旺角亞皆老街至登打士街一段彌敦道兩邊街道，共計有31間珠寶金行和錶行，如周生生、周大福及六福等。記者由昨晨9時至下午2時來回視察，都不見有警員巡邏。其間店舖陸續開門迎客，珠寶首飾逐一放到飾櫃，吸引途人駐足，但就是沒有見到警員。至於前日遇劫的油麻地上海街金行，昨日並無營業。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191225/large/1577203357_71f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191225%2Flarge%2F1577203357_71f5.jpg&h=5b1d5fe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n旺角彌敦道一帶金行林立，但是昨日未見有警員巡邏。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n肯德基遇劫失3.7萬<br />\n<br />\n油尖旺區議員林健文昨在一個電台節目上稱，近月軍裝警員在街上巡邏的情況幾乎絕迹，質疑警方稱要應付示威者而減少警力的說法，認為警方似乎在查案及偵破案件上亦令人懷疑，在處理近期多宗劫案有如束手無策。他又說，前日兩宗搶劫案發生後，曾有向當區警民關係科查詢，獲回覆雖未恢復警員行「孖咇」，但月初開始有以小隊形式到風險較高的地方包括金行巡邏。林健文相信，警方取消行「孖咇」，可能與市民近來對警方的觀感有關，但是他強調要防止大型劫案就需要作高調巡邏。<br />\n<br />\n另外，前晚11時許沙田火炭山尾街肯德基快餐店遭兩名持刀蒙面賊行劫，損失3.7萬元。<br />\n<br />\n■記者胡恩宏"},{"pid":"c99d0c481112a3dc8444e4e7a718b63448dce0c5","tid":1797198,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T08:27:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">無忘承諾 並肩同行<br />\n民陣元誕大遊行</span><br />\n日期 : 1月1日 (三)<br />\n時間：14:00<br />\n地點：維園中央草坪 ==&gt; 遮打道行人專用區"},{"pid":"597c5fd88bea843ba4f5d6272d32681dc0034ce6","tid":1797198,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T08:27:52.000Z","msg":"借個位嚟推廣<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂廁</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一齊將洗手間變成實體連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1796473\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1796473</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f9f53019895b2e385273154b1717db7b33e69725","tid":1797198,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T08:31:26.000Z","msg":"同7.21一樣"},{"pid":"400d981f5742e30000c82527db621c7aca2d192b","tid":1797198,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T08:36:40.000Z","msg":"無法治喇"},{"pid":"d97a95e89512c89413754d78aa8f1ceef8173cf1","tid":1797198,"uid":269515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T08:38:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KKYufO7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKKYufO7.png&h=009b227b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e2b549afc61d09ed8f4063b613e53af46759d045","tid":1797198,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T17:26:46.000Z","msg":"唔係呀，朗豪坊好多曱甴"},{"pid":"1a229db706461dca833afb9acf5687a256a6ffdc","tid":1797198,"uid":310461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T00:37:05.000Z","msg":"Maybe they are creating another round or in the process of setting up a series of BLAME later on protestors.<br />\n<br />\nAim :  to get support from  HK people if  HK people wants protect